iew.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs5608%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Not later than 90 days after , the Secretary shall establish goals for measuring, in an objective and quantifiable format, the extent to which Indian Tribes and Tribal agricultural and food products are included in the trade-related activities of the Department of Agriculture.December 20, 2018","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
